  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"About Game's Name\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > HRS Devil game is the well-known name of it, HRS is a shortcut of Horrible real street.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About This Game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the dark, twisted world of <i>HRS Devil's Game</i> (HRS: Horrible Real Street), where danger lurks at every corner of a horrifying maze. Your mission is simple: escape alive. But beware—the maze is filled with devils, skeletons, and ghosts, all determined to stop you. Will you fight your way to survival or fall victim to the horrors within?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966610/extras/dd5c986dfcf04359cbc195de97aba542.poster.avif?t=1735491522\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966610/extras/dd5c986dfcf04359cbc195de97aba542.webm?t=1735491522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966610/extras/dd5c986dfcf04359cbc195de97aba542.mp4?t=1735491522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>We present this game to see you playing and challenge with you friends and family and this game has many modes and features are making the game more funny and making you excited to play for example it has a \"finding mode\" and this mode which let you know what the first one who gets the key and opening doors to arrive to the win box and when you win in every mode it will give you gifts and player skins and we have a lot of modes are the same as the first mode but for each have Different ideas. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Remember: IN each map there is a one mode so you can't choose mode..</u></i></strong><